high_descs: Turn left and cross the room to face the sink.
Pick up the silver knife on the edge of the sink.
Turn right to face the tomato on the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Turn left to face the sink.
Place the silver knife on the edge of the sink.
Turn right to face the tomato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the counter.
Step right to face the fridge.
Cool the tomato slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn left and step forward to face the sink.
Place the tomato slice on the edge of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To cool a tomato slice plus place it on the edge of the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and head to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife from the edge of the sink.
Turn right to counter next to the microwave.
Cut the tomato on the counter.
Go back to the sink.
Put the knife on in front of the yellow knife in front of the sink.
Turn right to the microwave.
Pick up a slice of tomato off the counter.
Turn right and go to the fridge.
Chill the slice of tomato in the fridge and pick it back up.
Turn left and head back to the sink.
Put the slice of tomato on the counter in front of the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of tomato on the counter in front of the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the sink
Grab the butter knife that's in front of the sink
Turn right and look at the counter
Slice the tomato on the counter
Back up and look at the sink
Put the knife in front of the sink
Turn right and look at the counter
Grab a slice of tomato off of the counter
Turn right and go to the fridge
Cool the tomato slice in the fridge and then take it out
Turn left and look at the sink
Put the tomato slice in front of the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting a cold tomato slice in front of the sink
